key_products_services: Category-based item listings (vehicles, electronics, home goods, clothing, etc.)
Seller promotion and featured listing services

Fraud detection and trust & safety monitoring

How does seasonality affect different product categories?
What is the user journey from search to completed transaction?
Which acquisition channels bring the most valuable users?
